{"id":845489184,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"8 months, 1 week","timestamp":1668729888,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"18 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/845489184/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Rectangle Area","memory":"5.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int computeArea(int ax1, int ay1, int ax2, int ay2, int bx1, int by1, int bx2, int by2) {\n            long long firstRectArea = (ax2-ax1) * (ay2-ay1);\n    long long secondRectArea = (bx2-bx1) * (by2-by1);\n\n    //cout << firstRectArea << \" \" << secondRectArea << endl;\n\n    long long tmpx1 , tmpx2 , tmpy1, tmpy2;\n    tmpx1 = max(ax1 , bx1);\n    tmpx2 = min(ax2 , bx2);\n    tmpy1 = max(ay1 , by1);\n    tmpy2 = min(ay2 , by2);\n\n    long long IntersectRectArea = 0 ;\n    if(tmpx2 - tmpx1 > 0 && tmpy2 > tmpy1)\n    {\n        IntersectRectArea = (tmpx2 - tmpx1) * (tmpy2 - tmpy1);\n        //cout << IntersectRectArea << endl;\n    }\n    \n    return (firstRectArea + secondRectArea - IntersectRectArea);\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"rectangle-area","has_notes":false}
